<h2>Viewing images:</h2>

<p>For navigation between image files in the current folder use joystick buttons left/right or programmable button “9”. </p>
<p>To change orientation of the screen (Portrait/Landscape), press “Rotate” button.</p>
<p>To change brightness of the image use “1”/”2” buttons (to decrease/increase brightness).</p>
<p>To change contrast of the image use “3”/”4” buttons (to decrease/increase contrast).</p>
<p>If you press “5” button, the image displaying mode changes.</p>
